 间，道路塌方 4697 处，损坏路基路面 356 公里，公路中断 82 处，桥梁受损 111 座，通信基站中断 107 个，通信线路受毁中断 651 公里，供电设施损毁 450 处，农村供水工程受损 168 处，输水管道毁坏 303 公里，供配水管道毁坏 193 公里，河堤受损 3.2 公里，护岸受损 31.2 公里，电站淹浸 86 间，农作物受灾面积 6759 公顷，水产养殖受灾 452 公顷，预计直接经济损失约 58.5 亿元。由于灾害严重、涉及范围广，导致被困人员搜救难度大、花费时间长，截至 6 月 21 日 15 时，灾害共造成 38 人死亡、 2 人失联。 广东平远县强降雨已造成 38 人死亡、 2 人失联 _ 腾讯新闻"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-ad7386e17099166921f30f174a99ada0_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "68 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/659531375"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIm8vdtcrtppAGEAMaCTEwODg0MDM0MSDer9WzBjAAON0BQApyCTY1OTUzMTM3NXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1719037556.775859", "card_id": "Q_659314005", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 17}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "职场小聪明好还是踏实做事好？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "不理解「职场」：锅最多的地方不是厨具市场，而是职场"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/70/v2-4de0b82d352a98b90618e0345568b168_1440w.avis?source=172ae18b&biz_tag=Post"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "67 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/659314005"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Im8vdtcrtppAGEAMaCTEwODc5MjA0OCDwn8mzBjAAOBZAC3IJNjU5MzE0MDA1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1719037556.776180", "card_id": "Q_642657270", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 39}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "职场新人如何快速了解自己的工作内容？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.c